# Private RBN auth module (Aggregator-equivalent shortHash / h algorithms).
# Not shipped publicly — Aggregator's shortHash gates RBN abuse and
# publishing the algorithm defeats that protection for everyone, not just
# us.  Operators who want a Linux-native feeder currently bridge through
# Aggregator on a Win box; the sanctioned Linux path is an open
# conversation with RBN admins.
rbn_auth.py
